Company Overview of Sandel Avionics, Inc.



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Sandel Avionics, Inc. provides embedded software for OEM applications, and compact integrated display systems for fixed-wing and rotary-wing aircraft in the commercial and military aftermarkets. It offers SN4500 4-ATI and SN3500 3-ATI primary navigation displays, SA4550 4-ATI primary attitude displays, ST3400H HeliTAWS 3-ATI terrain safety systems, ST3400 3-ATI TAWS/RMI products, and SG102 attitude heading reference systems. The company also offers support services. It offers its products through dealers in the United States and Canada. Sandel Avionics, Inc. was founded in 1998 and is based in Vista, California. The company operates a regional support center in Charlotte, North Carolina; and...
Sandel Avionics, Inc. provides embedded software for OEM applications, and compact integrated display systems for fixed-wing and rotary-wing aircraft in the commercial and military aftermarkets. It offers SN4500 4-ATI and SN3500 3-ATI primary navigation displays, SA4550 4-ATI primary attitude displays, ST3400H HeliTAWS 3-ATI terrain safety systems, ST3400 3-ATI TAWS/RMI products, and SG102 attitude heading reference systems. The company also offers support services. It offers its products through dealers in the United States and Canada. Sandel Avionics, Inc. was founded in 1998 and is based in Vista, California. The company operates a regional support center in Charlotte, North Carolina; and a product support and sales center in Concord, North Carolina.
