Flat-rate pricing includes:

Full bench check
Update to the latest applicable software
Parts necessary to repair the unit (cases of unusual extreme damage will be quoted separately)
Recertification with FAA form 8130
90 Day warranty or the balance of the factory warranty, whichever is longer 

